    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the cold pack and it didnt do much. i really just want to take the advil so i can get some work done. if i just take like 200mg or 400mg once, is there actually a real risk of it messing up my kidneys right away? it feels like such a small amount to even worry about.",
